        {
            "title": "「小背心」許靖韻澄天一房收樓 前年550萬入市 單位享開揚山景「 感恩！也要更努力」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"「小背心」許靖韻澄天一房收樓 前年550萬入市 單位享開揚山景「 感恩！也要更努力」\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0c79271f4acf3ff01fc0a3eb559e923b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040314515745580.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">「小背心」許靖韻澄天一房收樓 前年550萬入市 單位享開揚山景「 感恩！也要更努力」</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英皇娛樂藝人、「小背心」許靖韻（Angela）近年轉戰內地發展得順風順水，前年她以約550萬元購入英皇國際旗下香港仔澄天1個海景1房戶，日前正式收樓，並於小紅書發帖分享。\n\n</p>\n<p>許靖韻於小紅書曬出新居客廳一角，從相片可見，單位開則四正，前臨開揚山景及市景。她在帖文寫道「感恩！也要更努力」，又標註「喜歡家的感覺」。不少網民留言恭喜許靖韻收樓，亦有人大讚「窗外風景很好」，並表示「感覺香港房子好精緻」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174940/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a079b337b5d722a64ab0330584850ced/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_14_41_56.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174939/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/85581e076e59db04cb3e3c7cd76861cf/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_14_41_56_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174941/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb24fef66e21bbfcb864632f90a0e305/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_14_41_57_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174942/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4a13dc9bf437ff37fb5245ff9784707a/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_14_41_57.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174949/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa1cbdf4b77d5d7195194e943bacb891/2025-04/PK250208SS06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>月供3萬 曾指要勤力搵錢供樓</h2>\n<p>翻查資料，許靖韻於2023年11月的首輪銷售期間，斥資約552.8萬購入項目大1房單位。據悉，該單位屬於低層，實用面積約325平方呎，實用呎價大約1.7萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>許靖韻接受訪問時表示，今次屬第二次置業，當看完示範單位後，認為項目間隔四正實用，故決定入市，屆時再決定用作自住或投資。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3007480/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許靖韻認為《施政報告》推出「減辣三招」後對自己有幫助，可減輕入市負擔，惟認為目樓價仍然好貴。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4fcf477cf86917b294c1f86f4f1a74ac/2023-11/WhatsApp_Image_2023-11-04_at_11_48_59_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許靖韻認為《施政報告》推出「減辣三招」後對自己有幫助，可減輕入市負擔，惟認為目樓價仍然好貴。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3007408/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"英皇娛樂新晉小花「小背心」許靖韻（Angela）現身售樓處。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1afe78a543ad6f764ba7244db2f900d6/2023-11/WhatsApp_Image_2023-11-04_at_10_56_30_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英皇娛樂新晉小花「小背心」許靖韻（Angela）現身售樓處。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3007409/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"英皇娛樂新晉小花「小背心」許靖韻（Angela）現身售樓處。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6af2ac71a8b6b289d6d857db3839beaf/2023-11/WhatsApp_Image_2023-11-04_at_10_56_30.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英皇娛樂新晉小花「小背心」許靖韻（Angela）現身售樓處。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3007510/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"據悉，許靖韻購入的1房單位屬於低層單位，實用面積約325平方呎，實用呎價大約1.7萬元。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d5cba37f7a1f435cb30ddc640b677ede/2023-11/WNP01P02251023_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        據悉，許靖韻購入的1房單位屬於低層單位，實用面積約325平方呎，實用呎價大約1.7萬元。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3007500/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許靖韻透露，首次置業以400多萬購入喜遇1房，目前作收租之用。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c27d42d06e9d619a75b0e28e07c0b9be/2023-11/169907137149598.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許靖韻透露，首次置業以400多萬購入喜遇1房，目前作收租之用。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>她續指，首次置業是於2017年以400多萬元購入英皇旗下長沙灣喜遇1房單位，目前作收租之用。另外，認為《施政報告》推出「減辣三招」後，對自己有幫助，亦受惠有關措施，可以減輕入市負擔。她稱，入得市都希望樓價有得升，惟認為樓價仍然好貴，自言要更努力工作來供樓。\n\n</p>\n<p>去年9月，許靖韻出席活動時候透露，單位月供3萬元，「對我嚟講都好大負擔，係好有壓力」，直言「要勤力做嘢搵錢」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/property-new/3288129/\">英皇小花小背心入市 許靖韻552萬買澄天大1房減辣降入市負擔</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
